arStrings.szText: "What could Mephisto want with Akarat's body?"
That corpse laid in the Spirit Realm for over a thousand years. Who knows how much power it holds now?
And Mephisto has puppeted the bodies of enough saints to give me an idea of what he’s planning next...
(sigh) We have to stop him. No matter what. Let’s find Eru, and get some answers.
